# Models

Read [docs/DOMAIN.md](../../docs/DOMAIN.md), [docs/TESTING.md](../../docs/TESTING.md), [docs/RAILS_STYLEGUIDE.md](../../docs/RAILS_STYLEGUIDE.md).

- Domain behavior stays in models; match existing patterns in the same model.
- TDD: `spec/models/` before behavior changes.
- Files under 150 lines; split if larger.
- No service objects or migrations unless explicitly requested.
- Do not run commands unless explicitly requested.
